content: How much do I owe in taxes?

Tax rate,Taxable income threshold
5.35%, on the portion of taxable income that is $32570 or less, plus
6.80%, on the portion of taxable income over $32570 up to $106990 plus
7.85%, on the portion of taxable income over $106990 up to $198630 plus
9.85%, on the portion of taxable income over $198630
